類似棋類有中國的'''田螺旋棋'''<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.langqiao.net/Article/Print.asp?ArticleID=501 |title=泰顺乡村棋类游戏 |access-date=2011-09-18 |archive-date=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711185424/http://www.langqiao.net/Article/Print.asp?ArticleID=501 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、'''旋螺运'''、[[旋回棋|旋回棋]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chaofeng.org/article/detail.asp?id=265 |title=潮人的杂棋 |access-date=2012-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304194205/http://www.chaofeng.org/article/detail.asp?id=265 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、'''呼雷炮'''<ref>[http://www.qxzc.net/gr/zhd/38-57/1954.htm 学而不专(1954)]</ref>、'''唿雷打炮'''<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://xzh1212121212.blog.163.com/blog/static/13847544520106634219208/ |title=安丰乡民间游戏 |access-date=2012-06-03 |archive-date=2020-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200822072129/http://xzh1212121212.blog.163.com/blog/static/13847544520106634219208/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[旋轉棋|旋轉棋]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fjsq.gov.cn/ShowText.asp?ToBook=216&index=12& |title=福建省志-体育志 |access-date=2011-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120507045824/http://www.fjsq.gov.cn/ShowText.asp?ToBook=216&index=12& |archive-date=2012-05-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>；[[朝鮮半島|朝鮮半島]]的[[轉車棋|轉車棋]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://053-054.com/total-home/p-home/kej/eonji/gona%5D.htm |title=자동차 고누 |access-date=2011-09-18 |archive-date=2012-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402142546/http://053-054.com/total-home/p-home/kej/eonji/gona%5D.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nol2i.com/s_5/s_51/jujae1_home1.htm |title=자 전 거 고 누 |accessdate=2011-09-18 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029190700/http://www.nol2i.com/s_5/s_51/jujae1_home1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.taean.go.kr/html/kr/intro/gunji/gunji_080201.html |title=물래고누 |access-date=2011-09-18 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/we